          <li><strong>RightLight 3 HDR</strong> — handles backlit windows without blowing out faces</li>
          <li><strong>5x digital zoom</strong> — stays sharp through 3x magnification</li>
          <li><strong>Windows Hello IR</strong> — face unlock without a new laptop</li>
